SDL ARCHON
==========

Description:  SDL ARCHON, as the name implies, is a clone of the original
(about 39-years old) ARCHON game.  It's a revival/update to the X Arcon Project from 1999.

Platforms:  Windows/Mac/Linux +anything else we can target that can use SDL2!

Requirements:  SDL2, SDL_Mixer, SDL_Image

Installation:  type "make" or read the INSTALL file (Spoiler, it just says run "make")

Documentation:  after installing, type "man xarchon".

Controls:  light side:  qweadzxc moves, tab fires;
           dark  side:  numeric keypad moves, return fires.
(Use Settings|Define Players dialog to change controls.)

Home Page:  TBD 

